  "texts": [
    "Compared with concurrent works, our approach focuses on a more challenging setup-DR tasks-and generates rubrics that both co-evolve with the policy model and remain grounded in external knowledge, enabling prolonged RL training with an evolving verifier.",
    "In conclusion, we highlight key insights, challenges, and promising directions for future work.",
    "Evolving rubrics adapt the verifier based on the policy model's capabilities.",
    "At each training step, we update our rubrics by contrasting the model's current rollouts, which helps the new rubric criteria better distinguish those outputs.",
    "We can view this as making the training difficulty adaptive to the model's evolving behavior."
  ],
